media:group.media:description:
💥[Please support me on Patreon]💥 https://www.patreon.com/cmkosemen
Join me on a regular day across Istanbul; where I explore a dead mall (again), run into paranormal mischief, eat, pet cats, eat some more, explore the city's strange back-alleys, visit an antiques bazaar, and draw alien creatures for my upcoming world-building projects...

Special thanks to Jakub Bobrowicz for inspiring this episode, by recommending me to film my daily art practice.

More on http://www.cmkosemen.com
